<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ページが見つかりません｜日々を輝かせる今日の一手</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@900&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 20%, rgba(245,181,49,.18), transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(160deg, #081d5a, #1a50c8);
    color: white;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5vw;
  }
  .code {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 10rem);
    line-height: 1;
    color: #ffd66e;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd66e, #f5b531, #ffd66e);
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
    color: #ffd66e;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    letter-spacing: .08em;
  }
  p {
    color: #e8f0ff;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    opacity: .9;
  }
  a {
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid #ffd66e;
    color: #ffd66e;
    padding: 14px 36px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: .15em;
    font-weight: 700;
    transition: all .3s;
  }
  a:hover {
    background: #ffd66e;
    color: #081d5a;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="code">404</div>
  <h1>星 が 見 つ か り ま せ ん</h1>
  <p>お探しのページは存在しないか、移動した可能性があります。<br>運勢ランキングのトップへお戻りください。</p>
  <a href="./">トップへ戻る</a>
</body>
</html>
